attributes.title: Horrible app experience :-(
attributes.review: I was willing to let many minor issues with the app slide, because I desperately require updates about our president. However, this is the most frustrating app I have ever seen. The app layout is an utter disaster, and it is the ugliest thing I’ve ever seen in my entire life. it drains more battery than I thought was possible in this reality. It is slow and frustrating and it makes the keyboard lag so far behind the rest movement of my fingers, that I can watch what I was typing 30 seconds ago appear on the screen. Don’t get me wrong, that is very entertaining, but I want to be able to see the words that I’m currently typing. I am so sad to half to be deleting this app, but if I don’t I fear that I will never be able to use my phone again. So, it is with a heavy heart that I leave a one star review on this application. It is horrible and terrible and ugly and useless and I hope it disappears so nobody else can go through the practically frozen phone that was losing charge faster than an android. I don’t want another good soul to endure what I had to endure.
